ENTITY

ENTITY

Your ^cInner Voice^n is a companion that comments on your actions and surroundings.

- It has an ^yattitude^n that rises/falls based on what you do.
- High attitude unlocks benefits (Tier 1 and Tier 2 assists).
- At high attitude you can rename it by speaking (SAY) to it.
- It can offer stealth hints, quick intel, and occasional utility.

^WSee also:^n DISPLAY, STEALTH, SKILLS
